-- HГҖM TГҢM NGЖҜб»ңI б»һ GбәҰN TГӮM MГҖN HГҢNH NHбәӨT
local function getClosestPlayerToCenter()
    local target = nil
    local maxDist = aimbotRadius
    -- LбәҘy vб»Ӣ trГӯ chГӯnh giб»Ҝa mГ n hГ¬nh (X chia Д‘Гҙi, Y chia Д‘Гҙi)
    local centerPosition = Vector2.new(Camera.ViewportSize.X / 2, Camera.ViewportSize.Y / 2)

    for _, p in ipairs(Players:GetPlayers()) do
        if p ~= LocalPlayer and p.Character and p.Character:FindFirstChild(targetPartName) then
            local part = p.Character[targetPartName]
            local screenPos, onScreen = Camera:WorldToViewportPoint(part.Position)
            
            if onScreen then
                -- TГӯnh khoбәЈng cГЎch tб»« Д‘б»‘i thб»§ Д‘бәҝn GIб»®A MГҖN HГҢNH
                local dist = (Vector2.new(screenPos.X, screenPos.Y) - centerPosition).Magnitude
                if dist < maxDist then
                    maxDist = dist
                    target = part
                end
            end
        end
    end
    return target
end

-- VГ’NG Lбә¶P KHГ“A Cб»ЁNG TГӮM б»һ GIб»®A
